<br>
The first leader seems to actually have been Venan, he was co-leader with Jaynus I believe but Kyri thinks Venan held the tag.  Venan was Valdria's brother.  When Jaynus left, Gray assumed leadership.  Jaynus was gone from EQ for over a year due to computer problems I believe, he did come back last year and rejoined the League before deciding he wished to raid at a higher level.<br>
<br>
I have some dates for the Gore events due to stories in the League Special Collection and due to Didi's diary, but by the time I joined the League Gray was already leader, and in the early days (before about January) I have no notes. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=carlluce>Carl Luce</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 166<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/14/03 10:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4898.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> An outsiders memory</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I have some dates for the Gore events due to stories in the League Special Collection and due to Didi's diary<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
