<br>
Guilds were permitted one week after FV opened--October 6th or 7th I think. And Venan was the official guildleader, and Valdria was his co-leader. Once they left, Gray and Jaynus shared power as co-leaders, with Gray being in charge of RP, and Jaynus in charge of hunting. Jaynus soon had to leave EQ, and left Gray as the sole guild leader.... It's all coming back to me now <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  .<br>
<br>
Makrazhat joined in November, and even at that time, Gray was uncertain as to many of the details of the guild's founding. I had asked questions along these lines in the general LoS members' forum--assuming they haven't been purged, you might still find the post, and the answers I received back then. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kaileena>Kaileena</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_whitespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#9900CC>I am Mod<br> 
